{"tid":1387241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［俾錢都要精明］泛民612基金唔做經濟支援，分散課金先係正路","createTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:01:02.000Z","uid":40250,"like":51,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"971fc7ae6da368c59a9874c283ab0a268b6697ff","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:22.000Z","msg":"本民前，星火同盟，杏林覺醒，由初一衝突開始都對抗爭者不離不棄，捐錢絕對要分散投資，要防止資金唔能夠落到義士手"},{"pid":"35a6d8fcf6b75a0a8fa212a1d6127ea6fff44d3f","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"997217504bdf5c8c1b0aea81bf0138bbd47742fd","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4791712574355b0100e783dd9a8db40e14e368c9","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:23:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a12c0c366da4952c6257c0cd236f95c3469a2fe","tid":1387241,"uid":64131,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"岩呀 dont put all eggs in one basket<br />\n不過呢度啲人你問兩句就話你熱狗"},{"pid":"9db51c5265da0e3031a8239819d043b49d61246d","tid":1387241,"uid":182088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:25:13.000Z","msg":"你岩"},{"pid":"43d805a68d0167feb59a30a43f41af22f09c3dd3","tid":1387241,"uid":34415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:26:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />課俾星火"},{"pid":"aa65420b1bceb529b4d0547512284146c4f68182","tid":1387241,"uid":138981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:26:55.000Z","msg":"612開始做埋經濟支援喇<br />\n<br />\n[支援義士途徑] 我今日捐咗喇 你捐咗未？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386958</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7b5c14f2dea9d1397975b8e21a4707472f2d20da","tid":1387241,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:38:22.000Z","msg":"求互推<br />\n[抛磚引玉] 所有連登軍師, 文宣入, (好認真!!)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dtfNgS\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dtfNgS</a>"},{"pid":"1180a8d3b0cee73b48796dbe8adb369006d8eaa2","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:15:27.000Z","msg":"民陣基金已經好疊水<br />\n唔好將所有蛋放同一個籃<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔同基金，有唔同專業人士組成，將錢俾佢地可以發揮佢地所長，運用d資金爾加有效率"},{"pid":"49b8e36e88f8d470b6cbe8a4937cb1b510a4f53d","tid":1387241,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:16:31.000Z","msg":"咁佢做咩支援要咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a7065f83ebb01125def5783da021f27e37857f","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:19:58.000Z","msg":"香港法制都講三權分立，互相制衡<br />\n<br />\n經過呢4年大家都好清楚有邊d人係做實事，值得俾番相對既支援<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而我更加希望星火同盟可以做一個中間人，當有義士需要經濟支援，你地幫手出post, 可以上埋黎連登出post, 同大家講需要眾籌，case by case咁做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我希望每一個真誠為香港付出既義士，都有國家退休軍人既待遇，因為你地夠膽企係前線，面對死亡同賭上未來，呢種勇氣同真誠已經值得我地支援到底"},{"pid":"8b4e63ab352f8f1d3bc0c8a56687f44565508ed2","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49b8e36e88f8d470b6cbe8a4937cb1b510a4f53d","tid":1387241,"uid":67813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:16:31.000Z","msg":"咁佢做咩支援要咁多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:21:50.000Z","msg":"法律支援，而佢地搵既律師全部收正價。<br />\n係我角度咁樣用d錢係on9<br />\n<br />\n錢唔應該咁用，特別係依家司法不公，法制崩潰既年代。<br />\n<br />\n對於受傷同被捕既義士要全方位咁支援<br />\n法律，醫療，經濟，心理上"},{"pid":"0c99fcf32995c419d994e407133f1179b508ea6c","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96709593c30e9cfaee29eefc05eba170348a731c","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:00:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec38dfbecece492b20b0da92f110ef53c4a4a013","tid":1387241,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n要幫一幫星火<br />\n唔問身份幫左好多人"},{"pid":"c163ac1001a9f62dbcfea78702f38083fcc2e3c0","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T18:00:33.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"d08c01cd091822dbe711807b68eb12a7558fb338","tid":1387241,"uid":232206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d78cd93ac1e98efb028e084af2fc410643940e","tid":1387241,"uid":92762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec38dfbecece492b20b0da92f110ef53c4a4a013","tid":1387241,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n要幫一幫星火<br />\n唔問身份幫左好多人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:30:20.000Z","msg":"有無星火課金既link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a072540180ef8280392695948e995e524e9eb97","tid":1387241,"uid":3775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1d78cd93ac1e98efb028e084af2fc410643940e","tid":1387241,"uid":92762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec38dfbecece492b20b0da92f110ef53c4a4a013","tid":1387241,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:20.000Z","msg":"pish<br />\n要幫一幫星火<br />\n唔問身份幫左好多人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T01:30:20.000Z","msg":"有無星火課金既link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T02:11:46.000Z","msg":"我出左糧！準備課了！"},{"pid":"623f997ed19daf27af4305c4be69ad2a78aaf87d","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:29:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fsparkalliancehk%2F&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=e07a59cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/sparkalliancehk/</a>"},{"pid":"f93442daed0d16054cd98314df72617cff603598","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:29:51.000Z","msg":"上FB入捐錢link"},{"pid":"8ffd9c20278adddabd0a85d4ffb99bbba356c463","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"你地自己有眼見，一有人被捕，泛民個反送中基金就即刻衝出黎cap水。 眼見連登多人話唔好剩係捐俾佢，就成班打手係到搞煽情，又post晒飛話捐左幾多俾泛民<br />\n<br />\n屌，我最希望每一位真誠為香港付出既義士，佢往後既健康，心理，尊嚴都唔會受損"},{"pid":"cc924079ba9a60bac2719ec92f9d689b1d63acc5","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5a12c0c366da4952c6257c0cd236f95c3469a2fe","tid":1387241,"uid":64131,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"岩呀 dont put all eggs in one basket<br />\n不過呢度啲人你問兩句就話你熱狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:33:59.000Z","msg":"嗱，依家無話唔捐俾泛民，係叫大家唔好捐晒俾佢<br />\n無得屌喇掛？"},{"pid":"308984044dbe9d00a698b19af4f7511666b6bcf6","tid":1387241,"uid":180268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:34:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1e69254387965636cb29b52aea59e5d6750544","tid":1387241,"uid":295300,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"大家自己上網訂物資<br />\n落前線派利是八達通啦<br />\n唔好成日旨意人代勞"},{"pid":"518cc4dcb1e7f54fee85d9a47d91dcb593d18ca2","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:58:21.000Z","msg":"係，要捐錢要俾錢既，要俾得精明<br />\n都係個句，依家係持續抗爭, 唔係永續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n泛民佢地想社運唔會完，等佢地有籌碼囉著數，所以不斷搞社運適當時候又散水<br />\n<br />\n但係今次大家都好清楚香港無得再退，只係你同我都好清楚呢場仗有撚排打，打長期場一定要考慮資源分配，補給同支援要點先做得長夠。 我地每次行動要有效率，務求以最少成本達到目標收工"},{"pid":"2e5fcf1d18a101719366422789ed534dbb754aee","tid":1387241,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:02:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fab41db60087723b391277e9221d89b798563cce","tid":1387241,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"呢個就岩啦"},{"pid":"f7db9f8a2ef3e55c1afff40de4464d86182f6dd2","tid":1387241,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"泛民真係冚家產"},{"pid":"92c73e861514e55932597aa667e6fbb2d51bacd4","tid":1387241,"uid":251292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:03:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4dc9fe2e0413cb701a288c4eaaf3d11da823b5ec","tid":1387241,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"支持分散投資<br />\n但標題不符事實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Krr2YCE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrr2YCE.png&h=871e0a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385833</a>"},{"pid":"1ad9d24d815e475d35029e7216707f0d9fe7d5e7","tid":1387241,"uid":250654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"絕對支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b20d19d769181c7f4127bab5d8db21ea131b709","tid":1387241,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"889f7ec311cbb7e199905c99ba649c30162b0d7f","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:15:15.000Z","msg":"我個人意見係<br />\n<br />\n設立類比退休軍人基金，係法援/醫療/經濟支援被捕義士, 佢地冒險付出前途同自由已經好無私，唔可以再俾佢地受傷害，感到孤立無援。<br />\n<br />\n同埋，希望大家前楚呢場仗既目標唔係特區狗官同黑警，我地面對既係一個殖民帝國- 中國。 <br />\n<br />\n搞不合作運動同持續既街頭示威，某程度係損害緊香港經濟，而傷唔到中國分毫。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">要贏一場一定要令對方付出更多戰爭成本，同時減少自己既戰爭成本。</span><br />\n<br />\n每一次要掘地搵架餐唔好搵公家既，最好搵中資既地方<br />\n要噴油寫字既，就搵中資既鋪，銀行同寫字樓<br />\n唔買中國貨，唔用中國銀行，遊行當日唔俾中資做生意，唔俾中資運貨。<br />\n<br />\n唔好再無目的咁佔領街頭同守路障做戰靶。<br />\n係依家無視警方反對，捍衛遊行自由本身就係一種好重要既抗爭，如果係要遊行同集會既，就需要不斷進逼警方，唔係行行下差佬封路就set路障阻自己前進。<br />\n<br />\n搵方法不斷消耗黑警既裝備同資源，同時減少自己友受傷既風險同成本。做前線既要夠勇，信念要夠強，硬碰唔到就做支援遠攻。<br />\n<br />\n我建議大家要繼續返工，星期一至五繼續令社會運作，繼續創造財富，繼續搵資源打長期戰"},{"pid":"5d1982985dd2cfcdd92dfcceb8dfcbab0acab73b","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc9fe2e0413cb701a288c4eaaf3d11da823b5ec","tid":1387241,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"支持分散投資<br />\n但標題不符事實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Krr2YCE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrr2YCE.png&h=871e0a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385833</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"一有人出聲即刻撲出黎cap水<br />\n呢班友真係笑大我個口<br />\n<br />\n香港地去到今日生死存亡既時刻，仲掛住個少少私利<br />\n<br />\n只係想問句，屌你老母，搵得幾錢呀？"},{"pid":"43138b21492a980b928247311a91f2457b4ac0a5","tid":1387241,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1982985dd2cfcdd92dfcceb8dfcbab0acab73b","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc9fe2e0413cb701a288c4eaaf3d11da823b5ec","tid":1387241,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"支持分散投資<br />\n但標題不符事實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Krr2YCE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKrr2YCE.png&h=871e0a6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385833\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385833</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"一有人出聲即刻撲出黎cap水<br />\n呢班友真係笑大我個口<br />\n<br />\n香港地去到今日生死存亡既時刻，仲掛住個少少私利<br />\n<br />\n只係想問句，屌你老母，搵得幾錢呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"嗰日不停有人話唔包經濟援助，質疑條數等<br />\n同其他抺黑post<br />\n先出嚟講啫<br />\n<br />\n如果唔講又話唔交代不透明啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c9cfa583041ca9fe90229efb2206ece785f187","tid":1387241,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"唔好直接比錢啦 買裝比佢地等佢地唔洗出自己錢買<br />\n佢地收左你錢 咪覺得唔衝對唔住你？<br />\n令佢地良心過得去唯一方法就係如果佢要裝我地就係前線擺低比佢 食就同平時一樣自己搞掂<br />\n<br />\n[個腦生屎？] 咪撚再講捐飯 、捐八達通  用下個腦啦 不服來辯<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385666</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我相信香港人好醒目<br />\n所以我地應該從根本解決問題=買裝比前線 買完直接擺底就得 咁先最最最快最有效<br />\n唔好中計<br />\n帶頭吹風搞捐飯捐券捐錢全部都係鬼，比d不知名人士（三毛藍絲）發國難財，仲要比<span style=\"color: red;\">警察有機會派人起我地既前線勇武義士底</span><br />\n<br />\n#香港人要醒目"},{"pid":"9986699a38e543d48b4758d3baa0caf387edb0ac","tid":1387241,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b73de3d7c2b1413a1752b35f28d845597db2768","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43138b21492a980b928247311a91f2457b4ac0a5","tid":1387241,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d1982985dd2cfcdd92dfcceb8dfcbab0acab73b","tid":1387241,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4dc9fe2e0413cb701a288c4eaaf3d11da823b5ec","tid":1387241,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"支持分散投資<br />\n但標題不符事實<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Krr2YCE.